movies.title: Superman
movies.plot: Mild-mannered Clark Kent works as a reporter at the Daily Planet alongside his crush, Lois Lane. Clark must summon his superhero alter-ego when the nefarious Lex Luthor launches a plan to take over the world.
movies.awards: Nominated for 3 Oscars. Another 17 wins & 19 nominations.

movies.title: Batman Returns
movies.plot: Having defeated the Joker, Batman now faces the Penguinâ€”a warped and deformed individual who is intent on being accepted into Gotham society, with the help of Max Schreck, a crooked businessman, whom he coerces into helping him run for the position of Mayor of Gotham, while they both attempt to frame Batman in a different light. Batman must attempt to clear his name, all while also deciding just what must be done with the mysterious Catwoman slinking about.
movies.awards: Nominated for 2 Oscars. Another 2 wins & 27 nominations.
